oyees themselves to submit projects they believe in.</p>\r\n<p>Each day, by sharing enthusiasm and smiles, Bel and its employees act on their conviction that small community initiatives can yield spectacular success. Our Foundation underscores this goal by helping to build a world in which everyone can grow up smiling.</p>\r\n<!--:-->', 'Ambition', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-27', '', '', '2012-07-12 09:04:44', '2012-07-12 08:04:44', '', 11, 'http://fondation-bel.draft.lu/11-revision-27/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ; 
